----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
WINDOWS:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Requisitos:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1-Tener gtk+ instalado (puedes descargarlo de: http://www.gtk.org/download-windows.html)
2-Tener instalado mysql (puedes descargarlo de: http://www.mysql.com/)
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Instalacion:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
1-Agregar usuario gadpime y password gadpime a mysql
2-Importar taula.sql 
3-Ejectuar gadpime


----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
LINUX:
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

